Paper: hep-th/9408045

Date: 1994-08-08

Title: Constrained Analysis of Topologically Massive Gravity

Authors: J. Barcelos-Neto and T.G. Dargam

Comments: 15 pages, IF-UFRJ-21/94

Journal-ref: Z.Phys. C67 (1995) 701-706

We quantize the Einstein gravity in the formalism of weak gravitationalfields by using the constrained Hamiltonian method. Special emphasis is givento the 2+1 spacetime dimensional case where a (topological) Chern-Simons termis added to the Lagrangian.